  "prompt": "What are some really good Korean spas in Minneapolis?",
  "response": "Minneapolis has several excellent Korean spas that offer a range of relaxing and rejuvenating treatments. Here are some notable ones:\n\n1. **King Spa & Sauna** - Located in nearby Chicago, King Spa & Sauna is a popular Korean spa that offers various saunas, pools, and treatments. It's worth the drive if you want a comprehensive Korean spa experience.\n\n2. **Shuang Hur Spa** - Situated in Minneapolis, this spa offers traditional Korean sauna experiences, including hot and cold pools, steam rooms, and various body scrubs.\n\n3. **Juvenex Spa** - While not located directly in Minneapolis, Juvenex Spa in New York offers a luxurious Korean spa experience with jade igloos, saltwater pools, and a variety of treatments.\n\n4. **The Spa at Hotel Ivy** - Although not strictly a Korean spa, The Spa at Hotel Ivy in downtown Minneapolis offers high-quality spa treatments and facilities which may include some Korean-inspired services.\n\nThese spas provide a variety of treatments that include body scrubs, massages, facials, and more, ensuring a relaxing and invigorating experience. Always check the latest reviews and service offerings to ensure they meet your needs.",
